Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出赋予皇帝Geass能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有妹妹 却没有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 是布里塔尼亚军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这栋楼的构造图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有识别号码的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这Knightmare还是不能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看服装是学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是军人吗 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快处理他的伤势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机密情报局的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下的直属部队怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 情报无误
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡拉雷斯的军队不知道我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以利用 这个数据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个幸存者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我吧 你的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,识别号码是QR5-YK1D6
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说发动Geass必须直视对方的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不老不死的魔女可没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在反击？恐怖分子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎已俘获我军的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但敌方是弱势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可否让我去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你只是暂居于此的客座将士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里该由我这个总督去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中华料理的调料不合我口味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狩猎人类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉身碎骨吧 布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 Q1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来去21层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P4封锁楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R5左转30度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N1 从那里向50米处天花板齐射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}埃米利卿 通信断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}IFF（敌我识别装置）代码变更
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}这是第5次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}欧提斯队 全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 到底是谁在指挥恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目居然是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 气度到底是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵部队 ZERO抢到的Sutherland还有剩余
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有ZERO在就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹会发生 会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该卡拉雷斯总督登场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 你不是去21层了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能两人独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11区的饵好像引人上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是C.C.吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第一个进来这里的圆桌骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连修奈泽尔他们也不知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚感荣幸 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为何让本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆桌骑士中只有你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目和Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…神殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这里是…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭神的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为阿克夏（Akashic）之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在神根岛对ZERO见死不救的你 有什么话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 你一直在骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说ZERO本是你同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说Geass的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我 你对我也用过Geass吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭曲我的心灵 让我服从你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心属于你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对ZERO的忠诚和仰慕都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 你该感到骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的决定 你的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算当奴隶也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我相信的是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身打扮你想穿到几时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看 变态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么对ZERO说话的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是对鲁路修说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚来了援军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量好多 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第4特装 开始降落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让中华联邦见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下之威仪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我神圣布里塔尼亚帝国的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面也来了 这下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡拉雷斯总督出现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃脱很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是我赢了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2波突击部队 J层以上压制完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团剩下的逃脱路线只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那里有我大部队镇守
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 就差把他们赶出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备报道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子最适合公开处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人应该确信已获得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,条件逐步成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差你那边的楼层了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10分钟以内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就以当前配置防守到底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪哈尔特的装置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都按作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是B2 发现敌方Knightmare一架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 刚才还…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B2 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人解除了IFF吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 这里是P6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人 敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是R5 R1被击破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 这样下去会来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你一个人先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来我们就是佯攻 是弃子作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光凭弃卒保帅的念头是赢不了布里塔尼亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 物资搬运口对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来这层 那里是捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疑似以Lancelot为蓝本的量产试作机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 但现在还不到捕捉的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 什么叫消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 你那边的楼层还没搞定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慌什么 那边不是有卡莲和卜部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这家伙吗 不安定要素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.09,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是朱雀 战略怎能被战术击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近战我占优势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是物理性因素 是别的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 你的真身是不是学生都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「光凭弃卒保帅」那句话 我就当真了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他是最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 拉克夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本大众 就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓四圣剑 绝非浪得虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是瞬间移动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也必须下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗憾的消息 准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 你所争取来的这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝无白费
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会自决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没文化的猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}全机失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}全机通信断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}…识别 变更为异常等级C
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs24}从截断处上升到1500后 开始回旋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了 这样就能把空中的敌人打下地面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错就错在封锁逃脱路线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这就等于告知了你的所在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 卡拉雷斯总督
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总督被打败了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,康威尔卿在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和总督一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那指挥系统呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说交给…内务省的文官？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慌张什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是夺权 只是临时措施
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以吾公主殿下之名起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们能合作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说科奈莉娅公主殿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我这就前往现场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥救援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔弗雷德负责指挥警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴特留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎么会突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是真人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人啊 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止播放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不接受信号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我设置的Line Omega
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道这个的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刮目相看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切拥有力量的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争与歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者炫耀着恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持错误不断流传的悲喜剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界没有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不得不复活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要强者还在继续凌虐弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会持续抗争下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先对愚蠢的卡拉雷斯总督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才 已施以天诛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 动作还挺快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人的国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查明了 发信源是中华联邦总领事馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非亡命过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样突破包围网的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们从倒塌的大楼里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以巴别塔作为道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 中华联邦是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先就说好了？不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是死了吗 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这是冒牌货？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 只要突入总领事馆…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是重大的违规行为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会引起国际问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然自称是ZERO 就是杀害皇族的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然和EU作战也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都是无底洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害总督和确保逃脱路线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然同时实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种智慧和胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与行使错误力量的所有人作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我在此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次宣布 成立日本合众国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有圣上的敕令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我的决定有不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO啊 只要是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合众国…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子建国？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这一瞬间开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间就是日本合众国第一块领土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个房间的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是那么有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不问人种 主义 宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为国民的资格只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是行使正义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里开始是我中华联邦的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日后外交场上见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底有多少利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是布里塔尼亚军 已经请回了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者你是ZERO的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 是哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对猜谜没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来取ZERO的性命了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐等无法改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找到并保护娜娜莉 我需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比皇帝比朱雀都强的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会获得的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵Geass的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必能创造出以日本合众国为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越布里塔尼亚的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.77,0:24:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此首先要将他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将那虚伪的弟弟 罗洛…
